Package: rauthoring
Title: An introduction to authoring literate programming documents.
Version: 0.2.5
Author: Laurent Gatto <lg390@cam.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Laurent Gatto <lg390@cam.ac.uk>
Description: An introduction to literate programming and reproducible
	     research authoring using R, markdown, knitr and other
	     packages.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: utils, shiny
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, markdown, ReportingTools, DESeq2
URL: https://github.com/lgatto/rauthoring
